inclusion.criterion: total serum bilirubin ≥ 6 mg/dL at 24±6 h of life
inclusion.label: met

exclusion.criterion: Those given exchange transfusion/ phototherapy within 24 h of age.
exclusion.label: not_met

exclusion.criterion: Anticipated to require neonatal intensive care or required neonatal intensive care for more than 24 h.
exclusion.label: not_met

notes: Uncomplicated neonatal jaundice that may require phototherapy.
